I had somewhat of an idea about #exotic, but I had absolutely no idea how to break an exotic choreo down to the T, I still completely don’t.

What I learned however is how to see every move as a prelude to the next, put on a character to tell a story, that every move needs to be paced differently, to technicals like weight shift, momentum, anatomy and then of course dancing 20 times in every class even before daring to call it an end.

#learning relearning unlearning… it’s pure rigour🤌🏽
